On Mon, 13 May 2002, John wrote:

> Today i tried to replace the CV gaiters on my bus but have come up
against 5 allen bolts securing the flange which absolutely refuse to
budge - any suggestions?

Make sure that they are really allen bolts.  They might be triple square.

Squirt some penetrating oil on the flange that the bolts thread into.

A hefty set of vice-grips can be your friend if all else fails.

George Lyle

